{"tid":1825589,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"暗瘡護膚問題！！！","createTime":"2020-01-15T11:55:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T16:12:28.000Z","uid":313435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a607f5caf054f306b4a145cb7c937f7d70240e","tid":1825589,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:55:46.000Z","msg":"話說小弟由中學嗰陣都有生暗瘡嘅問題 不過唔算多<br />\n多數下巴位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但近呢排keep住夜瞓 唔知係咪因為咁好似又生多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />尤其係啲粒粒，佢會慢慢變暗瘡<br />\n<br />\n1.唔諗住食藥嗰啲 因為唔太嚴重。但請問有咩方法少啲生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.同埋我想問下有咩洗面 爽膚水 同保濕好用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保濕我試過好多都唔太掂 而日覺得好笠。我用過UL&bull;OS健膚液 Curel嘅乳液 KIehl&rsquo;s 嘅金盞花cream同佢個咩oil free gel cream 仲有平時買到嗰啲蘆薈gel。除咗oil free同蘆薈唔笠，其餘搽完都好似好唔舒服咁 同埋有啲搽完會痕 又生暗粒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我應該係混合性皮膚 而T zone較油，但而日洗完面都好乾 但又好似冇啲爽身嘅保濕產品<br />\n<br />\n希望可以做到水油平衡！<br />\n<br />\n靠大家了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008ca09418139a9a4a5c912b5d95763fe7c867f0","tid":1825589,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"下世好彩D"},{"pid":"6230b8359294b773b9b992d3ec2cecbb9dbb8125","tid":1825589,"uid":313435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"008ca09418139a9a4a5c912b5d95763fe7c867f0","tid":1825589,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:56:59.000Z","msg":"下世好彩D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:58:07.000Z","msg":"請問師兄平時有用開咩產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2f03300b6c04fa8a274bb7135e6224110bd89a","tid":1825589,"uid":71508,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T12:00:41.000Z","msg":"KIehl&rsquo;s 嘅金盞花<br />\nRubbish"},{"pid":"c13b43126ae926f727